ing the reflecting elements among multiple IRSs is\npreferable over deploying them at a single IRS.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Dec 2019 16:22:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Apr 2020 13:19:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 20 Apr 2020 05:51:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-21"}
