ar-Parisi-Zhang exponent 2/3 for sound-like\nmodes, the Levy-distribution exponent 3/5 for heat-like modes, and the full\nFibonacci sequence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Dec 2019 17:52:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Dec 2021 16:02:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-17"}
