ory, and the\npreviously inferred disk accretion rate may be lower than the real accretion\nrate by a factor of $\\sim$2-3.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Dec 2019 19:07:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Mar 2020 00:32:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-15"}
