 and sub-mm observations are needed to confirm the\nexistence of such structures and to improve the current understanding in the\norigin of transitional disks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Dec 2019 12:23:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
